# Agora Business OS — Environment Configuration

## Required for cloud features

Set these for Supabase-backed login, sync, and backup:

```
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
```

You can also place the same values in `app.json` under `expo.extra` as `SUPABASE_URL` and `SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`.

## Offline / Libre Mode

If you leave the Supabase values blank, the app still runs fully offline with local AsyncStorage storage. No cloud account is required.

## AI Advisor

The built-in AI Advisor is free and runs locally from your own business data.
No client-side AI API key is required.

## Security note

Never place private service keys in the app bundle.
If you add server-side AI or other cloud automation later, keep those secrets in your Supabase Edge Functions or server environment only.
